OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1774879867
OL,3,CCoast to Coast is newest national trail
OL,5,FThe Coast to Coast path which starts
OL,6,Fat St Bees in Cumbria and ends in
OL,7,FRobin Hood's Bay on the east coast has
OL,8,Fincreased in popularity over past few
OL,9,Fyears, and it has now officially
OL,10,Fbecome a National Trail.
OL,12,FThe path passes through three of
OL,13,FEngland's national parks as it winds
OL,14,Fits way from the Irish Sea to the
OL,15,FNorth Sea.
OL,17,FThose behind the idea hope its new
OL,18,Fstatus will bring a boost to
OL,19,Fbusinesses along the route by
OL,20,Fattracting extra visitors and walkers.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G1/12
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
