PN,35302
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1774879867
OL,3,CCoast to Coast is newest national trail
OL,5,FIt was the brainchild of Alfred
OL,6,FWainwright, the famous writer of the
OL,7,Fguides to the Lake District whose
OL,8,Fbooks with illustrations of his
OL,9,Ffavourite walks are still used and
OL,10,Ftreasured by many walkers.
OL,12,FKate Young from the Wainwright
OL,13,FSociety, explained how his Coast to
OL,14,FCoast guide has inspired so many
OL,15,Fwalkers, "His skill in devising this
OL,16,Froute was immense.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G2/12
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,354,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35303
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1774879867
OL,3,CCoast to Coast is newest national trail
OL,5,F"He had such a skill of taking us
OL,6,Fthrough a natural line. He's taking us
OL,7,Fthrough the countryside that not many
OL,8,Fpeople know about. And this area is
OL,9,Ffull of old settlements.
OL,11,F"Wainwright said that this is a walk
OL,12,Fthrough the history of England, and he
OL,13,Fwas so proud of this route."
OL,15,FIan Nelson of the Wainwright Society
OL,16,Fsays it is the author's illustrations
OL,17,Fthat really capture people's imagions.
OL,18,F"He had a great eye for composition.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G3/12
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,354,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35304
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1774879867
OL,3,CCoast to Coast is newest national trail
OL,5,F"I like going out with my camera on
OL,6,Fthese routes, including the Coast to
OL,7,FCoast, and trying to recreate those
OL,8,Fphotographs in digital form now and I
OL,9,Ffind every time that his compositions
OL,10,Fare absolutely superb."
OL,12,FThe Coast to Coast attracts around
OL,13,F10,000 walkers a year.
OL,15,FNow a National Trail, Alfred
OL,16,FWainwright's initials have been added
OL,17,Fto the top of all the the route
OL,18,Fmarkers along the way.
OL,20,FThe route is also now marked on OS
OL,21,Fmaps so it's easier to follow.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G4/12
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
