PN,35305
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1774879867
OL,3,CCoast to Coast is newest national trail
OL,5,FWalkers on the route near Ennerdale
OL,6,Ftold ITV Border what they love about
OL,7,Fthe route.
OL,9,FOne mother with her children said,
OL,10,F"It's really important for families to
OL,11,Fbe able to come down and enjoy the
OL,12,Fscenery and the lakes, and with the
OL,13,Fbridges and the footpaths, and
OL,14,Fespecially people with dogs as well."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G5/12
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,354,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35306
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1774879867
OL,3,CCoast to Coast is newest national trail
OL,5,FAnother couple added, "And I think
OL,6,Fit's just lovely that everyone should
OL,7,Fget to access it the same as anyone
OL,8,Felse." "I think particularly these
OL,9,Fdays with young people, with
OL,10,Ftechnology, to have somewhere you can
OL,11,Fcome out and spend time outdoors is
OL,12,Freally important."
OL,14,FThere have been launch events all
OL,15,Fweek, starting in West Cumbria, where
OL,16,Fthe 192 mile route begins.
OL,18,FLocal Labour MP for Whitehaven and
OL,19,FWorkington Josh MacAlister told ITV
OL,20,FBorder, "This is an amazing part of
OL,21,Fthe world.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G6/12
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,354,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35307
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1774879867
OL,3,CCoast to Coast is newest national trail
OL,5,F"And when people come here, they fall
OL,6,Fin love with it and they keep coming
OL,7,Fback. So we want to see more tourism
OL,8,Fin the Lake District; in Cumbria.
OL,10,F"And we want to make sure it's
OL,11,Fdistributed out to some of our
OL,12,Fwonderful towns and villages outside
OL,13,Fthe national park as well.
OL,15,F"This national trail is all about
OL,16,Fdoing that. It will drive more people
OL,17,Fto come to the area, to spend money in
OL,18,Fpubs and restaurants and
OL,19,Faccommodation, and that's exactly what
OL,20,Fwe need in this area."
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G7/12
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,354,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35308
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1774879867
OL,3,CCoast to Coast is newest national trail
OL,5,FMaking it a National Trail has been in
OL,6,Fpreparation for three years, with #5.5
OL,7,Fmillion spent on it as part of the
OL,8,FGovernment's Miles Without Stiles
OL,9,Fproject.
OL,11,FBaroness Sue Hayman, Environment
OL,12,FMinister for Access, and former
OL,13,FWorkington MP, told ITV Border, "We've
OL,14,Fmade it much more accessible. So new
OL,15,Fbridges, taking out stiles, taking
OL,16,Faway gates so that more people can
OL,17,Faccess it.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G8/12
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,354,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35309
SC,0009
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1774879867
OL,3,CCoast to Coast is newest national trail
OL,5,F"We've also brought in loop trails and
OL,6,Fother trails that connect to other
OL,7,Fareas in order that more people can
OL,8,Fthen come and enjoy the walk, even if
OL,9,Fthey can't do the whole of the path.
OL,11,F"That accessibility makes a real
OL,12,Fdifference. And it gives access to
OL,13,Fmore funding so that the path is going
OL,14,Fto be there in good repair for the
OL,15,Flong term."
OL,17,FFrom St Bees the route goes through
OL,18,Fthe Lake District then through the
OL,19,FYorkshire Dales and the North York
OL,20,FMoors to finish at Robin Hood's Bay.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                 G9/12
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,354,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35310
SC,0010
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1774879867
OL,3,CCoast to Coast is newest national trail
OL,5,FBusinesses say it benefits them even
OL,6,Fif they are off the main tourist areas
OL,7,F- such as cafes, pubs, restaurants,
OL,8,FB&Bs, and campsites along the route.
OL,10,FWalking companies have also long run
OL,11,Fholidays for hikers to take on the
OL,12,Fchallenge.
OL,14,FRichard Duckworth, from Team Walking,
OL,15,Fsays, "it's a great experience for
OL,16,Fanybody that participates in the Coast
OL,17,Fto Coast.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G10/12
OL,2,W/.!+.!/*%/.!+,*%/T(,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BBorder NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,354,350,120,260,000,100
PN,35311
SC,0011
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F353A1774879867
OL,3,CCoast to Coast is newest national trail
OL,5,F"We've taken out people from the US,
OL,6,FCanada, Australia, New Zealand, all
OL,7,Fover Europe and many local people from
OL,8,Faround the British Isles as
OL,9,Fwell...It's our job to bring the whole
OL,10,Fwalk to life.
OL,12,F"Heading down to the sea at Robin
OL,13,FHood's Bay after two weeks and 200
OL,14,Fmiles. It's a wonderful experience.
OL,15,FVery emotional."
OL,17,FMore than 10,000 people a year are now
OL,18,Fexpected to take the route, enjoying
OL,19,Fthe views, exercise and fresh air.
OL,1,W{$~k4{$k4~sjw=                G11/12
